Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:00.65,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 说你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.97,0:02:28.68,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,工口松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:31.23,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,松崎 生理上厌恶松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:34.98,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来看不是抖M松吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:38.48,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:49.88,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到课桌和鞋柜里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.35,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有收到巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.40,0:06:13.07,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.28,0:07:21.74,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.51,0:07:43.35,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我桌肚里有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:57.36,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,笛子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:54.88,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,照桥同学 喜欢宠物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:39.17,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs50}注：日语中「干（架）」和「买（东西）」用的动词相同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.02,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,那片真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.09,0:23:39.01,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我是力 燃堂力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.68,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉放不下这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.68,0:23:42.30,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,在我心里 我们已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:44.39,text_up,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不会和你说话了
